Summerize results

Proportion of CSeQTL eGenes from GTEx Brain recovered by Bryois 2022

Configurations

configs = data.frame(cs_q_cutoff = c(5e-3, 5e-3, 1e-3),
                     fold_cutoff = c(1, 1.5, 1.5))
configs
##   cs_q_cutoff fold_cutoff
## 1       0.005         1.0
## 2       0.005         1.5
## 3       0.001         1.5
overlaps = NULL

for(i in 1:nrow(configs)){
  
  config_str = sprintf("cs_q_%.0e_fold_%.1f", 
                       configs[i,1], configs[i,2])
  
  fi = sprintf("results/step2_%s_prop_overlap_among_CSeQTL.csv",
               config_str)
  
  di = fread(fi, data.table = FALSE)
  rownames(di) = di$V1
  di = data.matrix(di[,-1])
  
  overlaps = rbind(overlaps, diag(di))
}

overlaps = as.data.frame(overlaps)
names(overlaps) = rownames(di)
overlaps$config = 1:3
overlaps_df = pivot_longer(overlaps, !config, 
                           names_to = "cell_type", 
                           values_to = "prop_overlap", )
overlaps_df[1:2,]
## # A tibble: 2 × 3
##   config cell_type prop_overlap
##    <int> <chr>            <dbl>
## 1      1 Astro            0.238
## 2      1 Exc              0.196
overlaps_df$cell_type = as.factor(overlaps_df$cell_type)
overlaps_df$config    = as.factor(overlaps_df$config)

g1 = ggplot(data=overlaps_df, aes(x=cell_type, y=prop_overlap, 
                                      fill=config)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity", color="black", position=position_dodge())

g1 + scale_fill_brewer(palette="Blues") + theme1 + 
  ggtitle("GTEx brain")

Proportion of CSeQTL eGenes from CMC recovered by Bryois 2022

Configurations

configs = data.frame(AF = rep(c("SCZ", "Control"), each=3), 
                     cs_q_cutoff = c(5e-3, 5e-3, 1e-3, 5e-3, 5e-3, 1e-3),
                     fold_cutoff = c(1, 1.5, 1.5, 1, 1.5, 1.5))
configs
##        AF cs_q_cutoff fold_cutoff
## 1     SCZ       0.005         1.0
## 2     SCZ       0.005         1.5
## 3     SCZ       0.001         1.5
## 4 Control       0.005         1.0
## 5 Control       0.005         1.5
## 6 Control       0.001         1.5
overlaps = NULL

for(i in 1:nrow(configs)){

  config_str = sprintf("%s_cs_q_%.0e_fold_%.1f", 
                       configs[i,1], configs[i,2], configs[i,3])
  
  fi = sprintf("results/step4_%s_prop_overlap_among_CSeQTL.csv",
               config_str)
  
  di = fread(fi, data.table = FALSE)
  rownames(di) = di$V1
  di = data.matrix(di[,-1])
  
  overlaps = rbind(overlaps, diag(di))
}

                           names_to = "cell_type", 
                           values_to = "prop_overlap", )

overlaps_df$cell_type = as.factor(overlaps_df$cell_type)
overlaps_df$config    = as.factor(overlaps_df$config)

g1 = ggplot(data=overlaps_df[overlaps_df$AF=="SCZ",], 
            aes(x=cell_type, y=prop_overlap, fill=config)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity", color="black", position=position_dodge()) + 
  ggtitle("CMC SCZ")
